{"tid":902972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"時日曷喪，予及汝皆亡","createTime":"2018-11-15T08:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T08:38:00.000Z","uid":132076,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"602f37a20cb0f0689ee204f4dc58e5291ed2dae8","tid":902972,"uid":132076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:01:15.000Z","msg":"美國話檢討香港獨立關稅地位，藍絲阿伯都開始覺得唔對路。<br />\n<br />\n連登反而一派幸災樂禍。<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞錯，無話咁做唔岩，我淨係諗起一個成語，同大家些牙下：&ldquo;時日曷喪，予及汝皆亡 &rdquo;。（咁樣嘅日子幾時先完？我同你一齊死！）<br />\n<br />\n以前夏桀就係咁比人推翻左，香港都唔奢望推翻港共定點啦，大家齊齊搭鐵達尼入北冰洋啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292e86f2e9b66e3237ec2c22672e182764272f76","tid":902972,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:03:01.000Z","msg":"今日特別多呢類Post，驚嗱？"},{"pid":"945e096c435248c33bc0ac9f7cc632e3e5bf133a","tid":902972,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zk61VCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZk61VCu.png&h=9170993c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9355fbb32ba9767cda6133184535032ca43b398","tid":902972,"uid":132076,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"945e096c435248c33bc0ac9f7cc632e3e5bf133a","tid":902972,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zk61VCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZk61VCu.png&h=9170993c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"so?"},{"pid":"6bf042f58c092eebf9bff1665ac02f6dde3aa475","tid":902972,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f014b17b5c2b92d967e7dbc46c3c68f8b246cf0","tid":902972,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bf042f58c092eebf9bff1665ac02f6dde3aa475","tid":902972,"uid":26451,"like"